title: Impossible Man (Marvel Comics)
description:
Ichthypod Productions proudly presents, "DCP Essential Impossible Man Vol. 1-4"!

Impossible Man is a supporting character in the Marvel Universe. He debuted in Fantastic Four #11 and has since gone on to hassle many of the Marvel Characters. DCP contributor, Lusiphur, is a HUGE fan who tracked down all of Impy's appearances and compiled them chronologically into the four volumes that make up this torrent.

A big hat-tip to the creative teams, the scanners and Lusiphur the Compiler! Secure it, scatter it!
